{"tid":521071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求片 臥軌自殺慘狀　女被斷腿掙扎數小時才亡","createTime":"2018-01-06T06:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T07:01:52.000Z","uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"824304960d901a8a46f4b8affd655e667aac05fb","tid":521071,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"中國山東淄博在昨日發生一起臥軌自殺案件，一名女子臥軌自殺，雙腿瞬間被輾斷，但她沒有馬上斷氣，掙扎數小時後才不治身亡，整個過程也被民眾拍下。<br />\n<br />\n據中國《梨視頻》報導，這名女子在臥軌前，一度被工作人員發現，而工作人員企圖阻止她輕生，火車駕駛也緊急剎車停駛。工作人員原本以為狀況解除，沒想到待火車重新啟動出發，女子突然衝到火車前臥軌自殺，雙腿當場被輾斷。目擊者指出，女子被輾斷雙腿後，還有氣息，民眾與站務人員也馬上報警，以及通知婦人的丈夫。之後婦人被送醫，但仍因為傷勢過重身亡。（施旖婕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180106/1273154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180106%2F1273154&d=sUHPyzpocB2%2BpF4k5qrO7XIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=03d7ebf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180106%2F1273154&h=c585c3b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180106/1273154</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180106/640_e1c9886018e5f5f2c965120fe1333293.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180106%2F640_e1c9886018e5f5f2c965120fe1333293.jpg&h=b18b1a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a3725485bff058f1d29a120b3d4d2f0ae42b12","tid":521071,"uid":131259,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"伸腳唔伸頭<br />\n強國人連自殺都on9過人"},{"pid":"1118e6f41c8f138d1bd8fa1e65163a33a71b2eae","tid":521071,"uid":28163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"救返<br />\n佢就仆街了"},{"pid":"4c530f74d34283b972744982e5e03badc38fd65c","tid":521071,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"